name: Library-basement
tagline: App to Recommend Books to Readers Everywhere!
body:
# Library-Basement
This is an app by 3 high school girls made for the Samsung Girls Who Code Mobile App Competition. Please note that the books listed were chosen by us, so they're pretty biased. We don't know how to help it search a database, so help us if you know!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
